*DirectFB-extra-0.9.16 (02 Feb 2003)

  08 Dec 2003; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> :
  Add patch to update imlib2 interface to new DirectFB #35250.

  13 Jun 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org>
